{
  "texts": [
    "We use GPT4o because of its effectiveness in generating structured outputs with Function Calling (OpenAI, 2024).",
    "The average cost of generating an insight with our method amounts to 63 cents, which significantly reduces the cost from manual insight generation of $140, i.e., the average estimated cost at our own company for a human-crafted insight (see Appendix G for more details).",
    "Also, potential decreases in LLM processing costs in the future will further reduce the cost of the system.",
    "For the Text-to-SQL model, we adopt the Lang-Graph Sql Agent (LangChain, 2024a).",
    "Following best practices to generate the queries (Rajkumar et al., 2022), the schema and 3 sample rows are given to the model."
  ]
}